name: CubeLabs
description:
Team Name - VolkillerGames

#Ue4Jam game  Knew i didnt have alot of time so i spent it trying out new things with materials hope you enjoy :D

Gameplay Instructions  WASD to move the cube around. Left mouse click to duplicate yourself to last checkpoint leaving a copy where you had been. Move camera with mouse and zoom with middle mouse wheel.

 Find the end of each level while changing color to open new areas
